{"tid":853734,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【日本】最喜歡的運動員排行榜top10","createTime":"2018-10-08T23:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T03:38:03.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"94a6fba48fd264bee16f1c7f873d94486e382460","tid":853734,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:28:54.000Z","msg":"『第11回 好きなスポーツ選手ランキング』男女別TOP10を発表<br />\n<br />\n男性選手<br />\n1.大谷翔平（野球）<br />\n2.羽生結弦（フィギュアスケート）<br />\n3.内村航平（男子体操）<br />\n4.宇野昌磨（フィギュアスケート）<br />\n5.錦織圭（テニス）<br />\n6.田中将大（野球）<br />\n7.本田圭佑（サッカー）<br />\n8.平野歩夢（スノーボード）<br />\n9.香川真司（サッカー）<br />\n10.田臥勇太（バスケットボール）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女性選手<br />\n<br />\n1.大坂なおみ（テニス）<br />\n2.池江璃花子（水泳）<br />\n3.吉田沙保里（レスリング）<br />\n4.石川佳純（卓球）<br />\n5.高梨沙羅（スキージャンプ）<br />\n6.本田真凜（フィギュアスケート）<br />\n7.福原愛（卓球）<br />\n8.藤澤五月（カーリング）<br />\n9.宮原知子（フィギュアスケート）<br />\n10.奥原希望（バドミントン）"},{"pid":"e17a04767ec24f0d3643a6c62a641d70135cc19a","tid":853734,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:33:33.000Z","msg":"福原愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f452012777f7909c3a6ff76699e8fb34aee9b1e3","tid":853734,"uid":43924,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T23:55:23.000Z","msg":"倉井空呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450e781068a7250563ae2f4eba6a8513b95eb05e","tid":853734,"uid":121177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"大谷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669b8bd105665fd478acedaa434e55679786457a","tid":853734,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:50:16.000Z","msg":"第9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk